{"tid":518776,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"老土都要講，大家真係要珍惜眼前人","createTime":"2018-01-03T16:34:05.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-05T13:39:37.000Z","uid":111422,"like":48,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":12,"replies":[{"pid":"97ae00bbfac07f3c2192bd6e201dd61662ee0aa7","tid":518776,"uid":111422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T16:34:05.000Z","msg":"平時成日見有巴絲講，都有D心up<br />\n估唔到會發生係我身邊既人身上<br />\n我舅母先得四十幾歲，琴晚哮喘發作送左入醫院，送到去醫生話個心停左二十分鐘，好大機會醒唔番，就算醒得番都會變植物人<br />\n平時佢同我舅父好sweet，成日一齊周圍去，post相上facebook。佢對仔女先得十幾廿歲，都未享兒女福就搞到咁。佢前日先同我屋企人一齊去食飯，仲有講有笑，兩日後就已經瞓左係醫院。<br />\n現實真係好殘酷，但無奈既係我地一定要接受。<br />\n老土都要講句，大家真係要珍惜眼前人，關心多D父母，出左事先後悔就無補於事。"},{"pid":"cc48cd67f4010a90629d4eb18d57b21ed525896f","tid":518776,"uid":46399,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T16:38:17.000Z","msg":"樓主加油"},{"pid":"7ee1231ee34472b3e5a75dfb6f2978d91ca46278","tid":518776,"uid":111422,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T16:39:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>樓主加油</blockquote><br />\nThx，希望佢醒得番"},{"pid":"823d6b6067d51082c22a97b7f2d306dc4cacc3b1","tid":518776,"uid":88126,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T16:41:08.000Z","msg":"➕真係要珍惜身邊人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f9f53d9d8ebd06045ca0f056489f6735f29e46c0","tid":518776,"uid":79081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T16:43:55.000Z","msg":"樓主加油"},{"pid":"0d8fc24bb4d045cc217b0230c356eddf2b179ab5","tid":518776,"uid":79081,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T16:44:11.000Z","msg":"希望吉人天相"},{"pid":"63c6e5d874329155b55a765396baa54d048b8fc0","tid":518776,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T16:45:50.000Z","msg":"氣管問題真係可大可少<br />\n珍惜之餘大家都要照顧好自己<br />\n香港好多人氣管有問題"},{"pid":"2eb035577187d1eae6f9f8aa20d74f55a7e3a799","tid":518776,"uid":111422,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-03T16:57:47.000Z","msg":"